'''岛之宫殿'''（Jag Mandir）位于印度[[拉贾斯坦邦|拉贾斯坦邦]][[乌代布尔|乌代布尔]][[皮丘拉湖|皮丘拉湖]]中的一个小岛上，由当地土王始建于1551年，完成于17世纪。王室使用此处避暑和休闲。<ref name=eternal>{{cite web|url=http://www.eternalmewar.in/User/Research/WikiDescription.aspx?Id=J|title=Jag Mandir|accessdate=2009-12-16|publisher=Eternal Mewar: Mewar Encyclopedia|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110721155828/http://www.eternalmewar.in/User/Research/WikiDescription.aspx?Id=J|archivedate=2011-07-21}}</ref><ref name=other>{{cite web|url=http://www.bl.uk/onlinegallery/onlineex/apac/other/019wzz000004211u00008000.html|title=Palace of Jugmundur in Oodipoor Lake|accessdate=2009-12-16|publisher=British Library Online Gallery|archive-date=2012-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121018162739/http://www.bl.uk/onlinegallery/onlineex/apac/other/019wzz000004211u00008000.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Mewar>{{cite web|url=http://www.udaipur.org.uk/tourist-attractions/jagmandir.html|title=Jag Mandir Palace|accessdate=2009-12-16|archive-date=2009-12-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091223184939/http://www.udaipur.org.uk/tourist-attractions/jagmandir.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Kishore>{{Cite book|last=KIshore|first=Dr.B.R|author2=Dr. Shiv Sharma|title=India - A Travel Guide|work=Island Palaces|page=466|accessdate=2009-12-16|url=http://books.google.co.in/books?id=COHI7LlpkSAC&pg=PA466&dq=Jag+Mandir&lr=&ei=5F8oS5H8D4iwkAT4-YnkCw&cd=45#v=onepage&q=Jag%20Mandir&f=false|publisher=Diamond Pocket Books (P) Ltd.|isbn=81-284-0067-3|archive-date=2012-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121024000255/http://books.google.co.in/books?id=COHI7LlpkSAC&pg=PA466&dq=Jag+Mandir&lr=&ei=5F8oS5H8D4iwkAT4-YnkCw&cd=45#v=onepage&q=Jag%20Mandir&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://rajasthantourplanner.com/Jagmandir_Palace_Udaipur.html|title=Jagmandir Palace, Udaipur|accessdate=2009-12-16|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090616100028/http://rajasthantourplanner.com/Jagmandir_Palace_Udaipur.html|archivedate=2009年6月16日|df=}}</ref>

